{"tid":1178372,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"連登仔喺度屌人飲喜茶睇支那劇真係得啖笑","createTime":"2019-05-30T11:02:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-31T02:47:30.000Z","uid":241832,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6a6e869b89bf5cf10069f047fb3bb2f184ed1d4a","tid":1178372,"uid":241832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T11:02:33.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n6月9日 反惡法遊行<br />\n銅鑼灣東角道<br />\n兩點半集合<br />\n<br />\n仲有聯署<br />\n</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n連選擇娛樂都要干預<br />\n憑咩擁有自由 擁有民主<br />\n咁同中共有咩分別<br />\n如果有得私下處 我相信你都要<br />\n只不過能力所限 你地只係有得block同屌<br />\n逼人表態嗰啲都係 <br />\n3個選擇得1個啱你心水<br />\n揀唔中又比你屌到上天<br />\n<br />\n喺cc台講預咗比人屌死<br />\n不過呢鋪槍口一致對外"},{"pid":"bf5b28396ac7957c995c4e2e8fc10b81e7a32f0b","tid":1178372,"uid":216985,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T02:28:05.000Z","msg":"唔係話乜嘢<br />\n祇係有得你揀都揀埋晒啲垃圾<br />\n其實好鶻突"},{"pid":"1080e8aa6e655e1389ed3f6c602710a9f7a9f71e","tid":1178372,"uid":241832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf5b28396ac7957c995c4e2e8fc10b81e7a32f0b","tid":1178372,"uid":216985,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T02:28:05.000Z","msg":"唔係話乜嘢<br />\n祇係有得你揀都揀埋晒啲垃圾<br />\n其實好鶻突"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T02:46:31.000Z","msg":"連登仔眼中有咩唔垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c64cafe676096471c184c36d87a29d896eedfeba","tid":1178372,"uid":216985,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1080e8aa6e655e1389ed3f6c602710a9f7a9f71e","tid":1178372,"uid":241832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf5b28396ac7957c995c4e2e8fc10b81e7a32f0b","tid":1178372,"uid":216985,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T02:28:05.000Z","msg":"唔係話乜嘢<br />\n祇係有得你揀都揀埋晒啲垃圾<br />\n其實好鶻突"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T02:46:31.000Z","msg":"連登仔眼中有咩唔垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},